---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="AKIULUMINART 2026 Closing Event: OTOTOE［音と絵］ | News | Takuya Asano"
  description="I will perform piano as part of OTOTOE［音と絵］ at GREAT DANE BREWING in Akiu on July 11, 2026."
  ogImage="https://asanotakuya.com/images/akiuluminart-2026-ototoe.jpg"
  ogUrl="https://asanotakuya.com/news/akiuluminart-2026-ototoe"
  ogType="article"
>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="site-title">Takuya Asano</a>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/works">Works</a>
        <a href="/news">News</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <article class="news-post">
        <a href="/news" class="back-link fade-in">← Back to News</a>

        <header class="news-post-header fade-in">
          <p class="news-date">2026.07.11</p>
          <h1 class="news-post-title">
            AKIULUMINART 2026 Closing Event: OTOTOE［音と絵］
          </h1>
        </header>

        <figure class="news-post-image fade-in">
          <img
            src="/images/akiuluminart-2026-ototoe.jpg"
            alt="AKIULUMINART 2026 Closing Event OTOTOE［音と絵］ flyer"
          />
        </figure>

        <div class="news-post-content fade-in">
          <p>
            I will perform piano as part of AKIULUMINART 2026 Closing Event
            “OTOTOE［音と絵］,” held at GREAT DANE BREWING in Akiu.
          </p>

          <p>
            2026年7月11日（土）、秋保の GREAT DANE BREWING で開催される<br />
            AKIULUMINART 2026 クロージングイベント「OTOTOE［音と絵］」に出演します。
          </p>

          <p>
            会場は GREAT DANE BREWING 2階。<br />
            高橋亨明さんの弾き語り、浅野託矢のピアノ演奏にあわせて、<br />
            中川和寿さんが即興でライブドローイングを行います。
          </p>

          <p>
            同会場に展示されているAKIULUMINARTの作品、GREAT DANE BREWINGの建物、料理、クラフトビールも重なりながら、<br />
            音、線、空間がその場で生まれていく時間になる予定です。
          </p>

          <p>
            ライブならではの空気を、ゆっくり味わっていただけたら嬉しいです。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="event-info fade-in">
          <h2 class="event-info-title">Information</h2>

          <dl class="event-info-list">
            <dt>Date</dt>
            <dd>2026年7月11日（土）</dd>

            <dt>Time</dt>
            <dd>Open 17:30 / Start 18:00</dd>

            <dt>Venue</dt>
            <dd>
              GREAT DANE BREWING 2階<br />
              仙台市太白区秋保町湯元枇杷原5
            </dd>

            <dt>Ticket</dt>
            <dd>2,500円（税込・1ドリンク付）</dd>

            <dt>Reservation</dt>
            <dd>
              <a
                href="https://qr.paps.jp/7rGaS"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >
                https://qr.paps.jp/7rGaS
              </a>
            </dd>

            <dt>Official</dt>
            <dd>
              <a
                href="https://www.akiulumina.jp/art.html#event"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >
                https://www.akiulumina.jp/art.html#event
              </a>
            </dd>

            <dt>Note</dt>
            <dd>定員に達し次第、予約受付終了。当日券あり。</dd>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script is:inline>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add("is-visible");
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.12 });

    document.querySelectorAll(".fade-in").forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
  </script>
  <style>
    .news-post {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .back-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      opacity: 0.65;
    }

    .news-post-header {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .news-date {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .news-post-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.6vw, 2.6rem);
      line-height: 1.16;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .news-post-image {
      margin: 0 0 40px;
    }

    .news-post-image img {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 560px;
      height: auto;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .news-post-content {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .news-post-content p {
      margin: 0 0 20px;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.72;
      letter-spacing: 0.008em;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .news-post-content a {
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .news-post-content a:hover {
      opacity: 0.65;
    }

    /* Information */
    .event-info {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 48px auto 0;
      padding-top: 32px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .event-info-title {
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .event-info-list {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .event-info-list dt {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .event-info-list dd {
      margin: 4px 0 18px;
      font-size: 1.04rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: 0.008em;
      word-break: break-word;
      overflow-wrap: anywhere;
    }

    .event-info-list dd:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .event-info-list a {
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .event-info-list a:hover {
      opacity: 0.65;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .back-link {
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }

      .news-post-header {
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .news-post-image {
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .news-post-image img {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .news-post-content {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .news-post-content p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.68;
      }

      .event-info {
        max-width: 100%;
        margin-top: 40px;
        padding-top: 28px;
      }

      .event-info-list dd {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
